{"tid":804483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"知吾知自己好撚戇鳩？","createTime":"2018-09-03T05:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T11:11:55.000Z","uid":31314,"like":16,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"080aa9dadabf410ac64aacf8bfe71ffc46fab1a9","tid":804483,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"我都忍左你好撚耐<br />\n日日扮撚哂大家姐<br />\n認真講 係F.1女仔最壞係我同凱婷<br />\n你要扮我地吾會阻止<br />\n哈 點知你越扮越衰<br />\n有啲野我同凱婷都未出聲<br />\n有時連班男既都未出聲啦<br />\n幾時輪到你出聲呀？<br />\n有啲野心照架<br />\n壞學生？你做到咩？<br />\n吸煙飲酒介手就代表壞囉<br />\n你連扣分 係學校搞事都吾敢啦<br />\n點做壞學生呀？ 小姐<br />\n你想學我地咋嘛<br />\n入黑社囉 係學校搞事呀！<br />\n最好學理我負分都要比人繼續扣<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾撚到啦<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系"},{"pid":"ea195ef87d7c215e0bd31ceb19762fb382a8714c","tid":804483,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"阿滿扮咩bb女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33027570a0a97480169261e3f9fe6d596d41c06e","tid":804483,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"我係包包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156febe164771c49c7d3aa9caf63702b2a8d0641","tid":804483,"uid":49055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8576dfa6faa7af8240ea4ad0f373d5dab4438c3","tid":804483,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"收到風 當年個作者d氣焰太勁 俾某兩個波台會員監生捉入公園廁所強姦 仲搞大埋個肚 後尾癲咗入青山"},{"pid":"d2482679417d886d3eb1797730d71a1b1f3a6db0","tid":804483,"uid":15236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"@@ 系"},{"pid":"13139f120e8dc38721128bcf31b87e108e1ebd02","tid":804483,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"1dae2f923d7ee3043d13aad2d82ab5fdba8a10